508
00:28:07,513 --> 00:28:09,694
in the hope that a smaller percentage of them

509
00:28:09,694 --> 00:28:12,815
are going to go on and buy either a physical or digital

510
00:28:12,815 --> 00:28:15,335
copy of their music.

