00:30:39,281 --> 00:30:41,102
And then there's the pro version, which costs $15

554
00:30:41,102 --> 00:30:44,785
and gets you a copy of Game Informer Magazine,

555
00:30:44,785 --> 00:30:47,687
larger discounts, and double the points.

556
00:30:47,687 --> 00:30:49,928
As you would imagine, anybody who's going to spend $15

557
00:30:49,928 --> 00:30:53,430
on a membership is a really good customer.

558
00:30:53,430 --> 00:30:58,253
And so the people in the basic free tier, on average,

