00:48:01,050 --> 00:48:03,951
but the sort of total value of what you

874
00:48:03,951 --> 00:48:09,533
are likely to get at the end of it is pretty clear.

875
00:48:09,873 --> 00:48:13,475
and people who are spending that much are thinking it through.

