00:48:22,439 --> 00:48:24,519
And even the first time going into nationals,

879
00:48:24,519 --> 00:48:27,681
there were all sorts of sort of hidden and unexpected costs

880
00:48:27,681 --> 00:48:33,323
where I had to, you know, suddenly pay for warm-up time and other things.

881
00:48:33,323 --> 00:48:34,204
I think, you know,

882
00:48:34,964 --> 00:48:37,026
every time you're making a choice,

883
00:48:37,026 --> 00:48:40,368
you're looking at it on the face of it.

