00:49:59,490 --> 00:50:02,352
So I don't think saying something.

916
00:50:03,151 --> 00:50:06,592
An element that makes it more enjoyable for you to play,

917
00:50:06,592 --> 00:50:09,693
and enjoyable to spend, that's making the game into a spend,

918
00:50:09,693 --> 00:50:13,334
is part of the entertainment of what you're doing.

